User Data Deletion Instructions

OptimaAI respects user privacy and provides a simple process for requesting deletion of personal data.

1. How to Request Data Deletion
Users may request deletion of their personal data by sending an email to:

w.mugwe@yahoo.com

2. Required Information
Please include the following in your request:
- Your WhatsApp phone number
- A clear statement requesting data deletion

3. Processing Time
All valid data deletion requests will be processed within 7 days.

4. Data Covered
This request applies to any personal data processed through interactions with our WhatsApp Business account, including message content and metadata.

5. Confirmation
Once the deletion request has been completed, the user may receive confirmation via email.

If you have any questions regarding data deletion, please contact us using the email above.
